text: Youssef Lemrini (born January 1, 1960 in Salé) is a Moroccan former football player and current football manager. Lemrini played at Mouloudia Club Lakouablia, and managed COD Meknès and Olympic Club de Safi. Since 2013 he has been managing Renaissance Sportive de Berkane. == Other websites == * Youssef Lemrini at Eurosport Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Football managers Category:Moroccan footballers
